Code.NativeIaC:
```bicep
// Bicep: Deploy a Databricks workspace with secure cluster connectivity (No Public IP)
resource workspace 'Microsoft.Databricks/workspaces@2023-02-01' = {
  name: '<example_resource_name>'
  location: resourceGroup().location
  sku: {
    name: 'premium'
  }
  properties: {
    managedResourceGroupId: '/subscriptions/<example_resource_id>/resourceGroups/<example_resource_name>'
    parameters: {
      enableNoPublicIp: {
        value: true // CRITICAL: Deploys cluster nodes without public IP addresses
      }
    }
  }
}
```

Code.Terraform:
```hcl
# Terraform: Databricks workspace with secure cluster connectivity (No Public IP)
resource "azurerm_databricks_workspace" "<example_resource_name>" {
  name                = "<example_resource_name>"
  resource_group_name = "<example_resource_name>"
  location            = "<region>"
  sku                 = "premium"

  custom_parameters {
    no_public_ip = true # CRITICAL: Deploys cluster nodes without public IP addresses
  }
}
```
